@startuml UEORMS_Sequence_03
!pragma teoz true
autonumber
hide footbox

actor Employee
boundary "Web/Mobile Client" as Client
control "Express API Layer\n(app.js route orchestration)" as API
control "Auth + RBAC\n(requireAuth / permission middleware)" as AuthRBAC
control "Subscription Entitlement\n(requireModuleEntitlement)" as Entitlement
database "PostgreSQL via Prisma" as DB

== 3) Cross-Cutting Guard Flow (all secured modules) ==
Employee -> Client : Access module endpoint
Client -> API : any /api/{module}
API -> AuthRBAC : requireAuth + permission check
AuthRBAC --> API : user context
API -> Entitlement : verify module included in active subscription
Entitlement -> DB : Subscription + SubscriptionItem + Plan lookup
DB --> Entitlement : entitlement decision
Entitlement --> API : allowed / forbidden
API --> Client : proceed or 403


@enduml